  <span id="freeText35081299276776234" style="display:none">Absolutely amazing. Anyone interested in ancient history or military fiction simply must read "Gates of Fire." By Zeus, this is one of those books that everyone should read, regardless of what their favorite genre is. Steven Pressfield has an amazing gift for transplanting the reader into his era of choice.<br /><br />I could attempt to spend hours writing a witty review, but ultimately it would not do this book justice. So do yourself a favor and add it to your "To Read" shelf, or the gods will surely curse you and your offspring from this day until the end of time.<br /><br />Get your copy here: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://amzn.to/2KBFAty">https://amzn.to/2KBFAty</a></span>
