<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/78127.On_Killing"><img alt="On Killing: The Psychological Cost of Learning to Kill in War and Society" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1373461495l/78127._SX98_.jpg" />
